            <img class="to-animate" src="/assets/kyle-yelling.png" alt="Kyle Yelling" />
            <p class="comic-book-bubble comic-book-cta to-animate">Check out my...</p>
            <a href="https://kylecoberly.github.io/resume/" class="to-animate comic-book-bubble resume">Resume!</a>
            <a href="https://kylecoberly.github.io/education-work-sample/" class="to-animate comic-book-bubble work-sample">Education Work Samples!</a>
