    {{#content "manifestos"}}
        <section id="manifestos">
          <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Some Things I Believe About:</h2>
            <nav>
              <ul>
                <li><a href="#" class="active education-link">Education</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="business-link">Business</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="software-link">Software</a></li>
              </ul>
            </nav>
            <section id="education" class="manifesto active">
              <h3>Education</h3>
              <p>The three cornerstones of formal education should be:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Curriculum</strong>, structuring the learning process to maximize success</li>
                <li><strong>Community</strong>, engaging learners with peers</li>
                <li><strong>Coaches</strong>, human beings who are invested in the outcomes of learners</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Education should ensure fixed mastery and embrace variable time</p>
              <p>Educational experiences should be humanist, meaning:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Educating the whole person</li>
                <li>Coaches and learners being authentic</li>
                <li>Empowering learners with choice and freedom</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            <section id="business" class="manifesto">
              <h3>Business</h3>
              <p>Businesses should prefer:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Flows over batches</li>
                <li>Purpose over profit</li>
                <li>Measuring impact over measuring time</li>
                <li>Self-organized cross-functional teams over top-down function silos</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Futhermore:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>People and computers are compliments, not substitutes</li>
                <li>People should not be scored or sorted</li>
                <li>Businesses should not automate processes they don't understand</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
            <section id="software" class="manifesto">
              <h3>Software</h3>
              <p>I believe:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>All 4 values and all 12 principles of the <a href="https://agilemanifesto.org/" target="_BLANK">Agile Manifesto</a>, as well as the 4 principles of <a href="http://modernagile.org/" target="_BLANK">Modern Agile</a></li>
                <li>User experience, visual design, and programming are fundamentally inseparable parts of application development, and all of them are part of an application developer's job</li>
                <li>Nothing is more expensive than poor quality</li>
                <li>The best interface is no interface</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
          </div>
        </section>
